_header: I see there is but little trust
Subjects: women, faithlessness of; transitoriness, of world
_description: On Woman’s faithlessness — one stanza rhyme royal

CULKk630.First Lines:
I se ryght well ther is but lytill trustOn to this world ay so full
                    of bruttylte…
CULKk630.Last Lines:
Thus ham I rokyd hydyr & thederThe deuyll sett fyer on all to
                    geder
